Privacy Policy

This privacy policy describes how your VideoUploader application (the “Application”) handles personal data collected from users. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the information you provide.

1. Collection of information
We do not collect personal data from users. The only data we process is related to authenticating your Instagram account through the video publishing API. This data includes:

Instagram access tokens.
The identifier of your Instagram account.
2. use of the information
We use the data provided solely to perform the following functions:

Publishing videos to your Instagram account on your behalf via the API.
We do not share or sell your data to third parties.

3. Data Storage
We do not store user data on servers. All tokens and identifiers are processed locally on your device.

4. Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information provided from unauthorized access and data leakage.

5. Changes to Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to change this privacy policy at any time. Changes will be effective when they are posted on our website.

6. Contact Information
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at developer7885@gmail.com.

